domain heattransfer
OutputManager tstep_all dofman_all element_all
ncrosssect 0 nmat 0 nbc 0 nic 0 nltf 1
PiecewiseLinFunction 1 nPoints 5 t 5 0. 10. 20. 200. 12000. f(t) 5 1. 1. 1. 20. 20.
